  "text": "It is believed that for each of these backgrounds there is a matrix description, which may provide a theory for resolving the singularity. For this claim to be valid, it is important to check whether these backgrounds are stable. Here we take an approach similar to that of [CITATION_1] . Consider there be some gravitational sources, localized in x − dimension as well as in the transverse dimensions. The existence of such sources will change the background.",
